   <conbody>
      <p class="- topic/p ">Multiple Qualifications and Benefits is an additional type of setup for the Reward Saving Program, where multiple products can be defined as qualification criteria and as benefit products. You can enable different ways to calculate qualifiers and benefits for a particular time period. You can set up multiple qualifications and benefits for a program to combine one or more qualification products to determine revenue and define benefits/price that needs to be offered.</p>
